These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-1::.
4 different games are played: go, backgammon, domino, poker
House: cottage, craftsman, farmhouse, futuristic
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, alhambra, tiparillo, vegafina
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, snowmobile, train, bus
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, may, june, october
 1. the blend-smoker is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 2. the craftsman house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 3. the futuristic house is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 5. the person driving the van is the person playing go##1
 6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 7. the person driving the train is on the right of the person playing go##1
 8. the person playing domino is on the left of the cottage house##1
 9. the tiparillo-smoker is the person playing go##1
10. the person who's birthday is in june is the alhambra-smoker##1
11. the cottage house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Game          | backgammon    | domino      | go  | poker     |
| House         | futuristic    | farmhouse   | cottage | craftsman      |
| Cigar   | alhambra       | blend | tiparillo     | vegafina    |
| Transport   | bus | snowmobile         | van  | train    |
| Birthday           | june      | october       | january | may |

