.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, social-worker, videographer, journalist
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, corn, avocado, apple
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, green, blood-red, chestnut
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, van, car, trike
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, july, december, october
 1. the person eating corn is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 2. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 4. the journalist is on the far right##1
 5. the librarian is on the right of the social-worker##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the videographer##1
 7. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
 8. the person driving the van is the person who likes chestnut##1
 9. the person eating avocado is the person who likes blood-red##1
10. the person who likes apricot is on the far right##1
11. the videographer is on the left of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| Job      | social-worker      | librarian     | videographer    | journalist |
| Food   | broccoli | corn   | avocado   | apple           |
| Color   | green  | chestnut     | blood-red    | apricot         |
| Transport           | trike         | van | car     | bus        |
| Birthday         | january     | october  | july | december       |

