There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, mauve, light-blue, green
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, juice, water, mirinda
City: liverpool, colone, edinburgh, venice
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, zombie, thriller, romance
 1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left##1
 2. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 3. the electrician is the person drinking mirinda##1
 4. the photographer is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 5. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the software-developer##1
 6. the person watching romance movies is the electrician##1
 7. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
 8. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 9. the person who likes green is the person drinking juice##1
10. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person drinking water##1
11. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person drinking water##1
12. the electrician is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| Job          | architect    | software-developer      | electrician  | photographer   |
| Color   | green     | light-blue      | mauve | amber      |
| Beverage           | juice       | milk         | mirinda  | water         |
| City         | liverpool | colone | edinburgh  | venice |
| Movie-Genre     | thriller       | animation         | romance   | zombie        |

