 7. the person traveling to venice is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
 9. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
10. the colonial house is on the far right##1
11. the modern house is on the far left##1
12. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

