The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, hip-hop, punk, electronic
House: art-deco, colonial, futuristic, craftsman
 1. the person driving the motorbike is the craftsman house##1
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left##1
 3. the fan of hip-hop is on the far right##1
 4. the colonial house is the bolivar-smoker##1
 5. the colonial house is on the right of the game-smoker##1
 6. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1
 7. the futuristic house is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 8. the craftsman house is the person driving the motorbike##1
 9. the oliveros-smoker is the futuristic house##1
10. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the craftsman house##1
11. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the craftsman house##1
12. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1
13. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
14. the fan of punk is on the right of the fan of electronic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Cigar          | montecristo       | game     | bolivar     | oliveros  |
