 1. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 2. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
 3. the owner of the frog is the fan of reggae##1
 4. the pilot is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
 5. the police-officer is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 6. the person playing snooker is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 7. the person traveling to hannover is the fan of reggae##1
 8. the fan of indie is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 9. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1
10. the fan of d&b is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
11. the owner of the ferret is the photographer##1
12. the person playing poker is the person traveling to venice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |      4      |
