 4. the pakistani is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
 5. the person eating pumpkin is on the far right##1
 6. the fan of country is on the far left##1
 7. the futuristic house is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
 8. the person eating papaya is on the right of the palace house##1
 9. the pakistani is the person eating kiwi##1
10. the thai is the person who growsazalea##1
11. the person eating apricot is on the left of the fan of folk##1
12. the german is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Nationality    | pakistani     | british  | thai       | german      |
| Music-Genre       | country    | hip-hop        | classical  | folk      |
| House         | palace  | futuristic | ranch-style | art-deco |
| Flower         | daisy | zinnia          | azalea         | tulip      |
| Food   | kiwi     | papaya     | apricot       | pumpkin          |

