.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, fonseca, blend, alhambra
4 different games are played: go, backgammon, whist, poker
City: berlin, new-york, hamburg, rome
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, videographer, nurse, police-officer
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, october, january, july
 1. the nurse is on the far left##1
 2. the fonseca-smoker is the person traveling to rome##1
 3. the blend-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 4. the police-officer is on the left of the fisherman##1
