 6. the person playing poker is the alhambra-smoker##1
 7. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
 8. the fisherman is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is the person traveling to hamburg##1
10. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left##1
11. the havana-smoker is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
12. the person playing poker is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1

