 2. the person drinking milk is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 3. the person traveling to berlin is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 4. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
 5. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
 6. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
 7. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 8. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 9. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
10. the person who growsdaffodil is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
11. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
12. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
13. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1

